%F A029336 a(n) = floor((n^3+42*n^2+372*n+1404)/10080 + ((n mod 4)-2)^2*n/96 + (((n+3) mod 4) - (n mod 4))/8 + ((4*n^3+3*n^2+3*n+1) mod 5)/5 + ((4*n^3+4*n+2) mod 7)/7). - _Hoang Xuan Thanh_, Apr 19 2026
